<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/module/toolbox.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/module/headerModule.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/module/infoCardModule.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/userHome.css" />
		<title>Document</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="main-header">
			<a href="/home" class="main-header-logo">Reviewdangil</a>
			<div class="main-header-left-element">
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/mypage" class="white-a">계정 관리</a></li>
					<li>
						<a href="/login" class="white-a">로그아웃</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<img src="https://picsum.photos/200/300" alt="프로필 이미지" />
			</div>
		</header>
		<main>
			<section id="left-container" style="background-color: red">
				<div id="address-input-container">
					<input
						type="text"
						class="text-input"
						id="address-input"
						placeholder="위치 입력"
					/>
					<a href="#" class="white-a">리뷰 검색</a>
				</div>
				<div id="map">
					<img
						src="https://img.hankyung.com/photo/202304/01.33299158.1.png"
						style="object-fit: cover; width: 100%; height: 100%"
					/>
				</div>
				<div id="bottom-buttons-container">
					<a href="review-write" class="white-a">리뷰 쓰기</a>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section id="right-container">
				<h1>현 위치 최근 리뷰</h1>
				<div id="info-container">
					<a href="/review-read">
						<div class="info-card">
							<img src="https://picsum.photos/200" alt="썸네일" />
							<div class="info-card-text">
								<span>리뷰 제목</span>
								<span class="review-text-thumbnail">
									리뷰 내용 어쩌고 저쩌고 어쩌고 저쩌고 리뷰
									내용 어쩌고 저쩌고 어쩌고 저쩌고 리뷰 내용
									어쩌고 저쩌고 어쩌고 저쩌고
								</span>
								<span>위치</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</a>
				</div>
				<a href="/more-review" class="white-a" id="more-info-button">
					리뷰 더보기
				</a>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
